        p.
                Now it's Wednesday, and I've done basically nothing since
                Christmas. Blair and Susan are both out of town, Hanna just got
                back today, there's no school, and things are getting pretty
                boring. I'm going to try to get out and get a haircut tomorrow,
                but I've been saying that for about a month, so we'll see.
